Improving explanation by instances has a major scope for improvement, by incorporating KB knowledge (for improving precision) or scraping list pages from search results (for improving recall). In Section (ref) we indicate ad-hoc mechanism to identify existing contextualizations in present KB-QA systems. This can be further expanded independently or CNPs from text could be useful in identifying relevant semantic qualifiers in the KB.